Package net.getnova.backend.json

Class JsonBuilder

java.lang.Object
net.getnova.backend.json.JsonBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
JsonSerializable
public final class JsonBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
implements JsonSerializable
The JsonBuilder is a tool to create JsonObject or a Json as a String without declaring any variables.
Example: 

 final JsonObject json = JsonBuilder
    .create("name", "Max")
    .add("age", 43)
    .build();
or 

 final String json = JsonBuilder
    .create("name", "Max")
    .add("age", 43)
    .toString();
See Also:
JsonSerializable, JsonObject
